ddot.it/this ..content.. W3C RDF/XML syntax test for xml:lang scoping. A single rdf:Description about http://example.org/node with one property using rdf:parseType="Literal" whose content is "chat", showing that an in-scope xml:lang applies to rdf:parseType="Literal" content. Author: Dave Beckett.
ddot.it/this ..tests.. In-scope xml:lang applied to rdf:parseType="Literal" (XML literal) element content.
